    <releaseNotes>
    - Added log off option. This requires appropriate permissions to manage sessions on the remote server.
    - Added a feature to list remote sessions and provide limited management of them.
    - Support for monitor spanning of full screen sessions.
    - Show the source of inheritance when "Inherit from parent" is checked.
    - Added connect to console setting to Connect As dialog.
    - Added audio quality and audio capture redirection settings (supported by 6.1 remote desktop).
    - Added "full screen" remote desktop size setting.
    - Global settings are now auto saved if needed (previously only the files were auto saved).
    - Name sorting is now similar to explorer where consecutive digits are treated as single numbers
    - Added comment field to servers and groups
    - Fixed redraw bugs when moving a server from one group to another.
    - Fixed bug where groups wouldn't always sort when making changes.
    - Fixed Connected group disconnect redraw bug.
    - Fixed bug where client size wasn't maintained when server tree visibility was changed.
    - Fixed a redraw bug involving "no effect" drag-and-drop.
    - Fixed a bug where password changes weren't always saved.
    - Fixed bug with not being able to exit if a document couldn't be saved during shutdown.
    - Fixed a bug where files were not being auto saved when the auto save option was selected.
    - Fixed remote desktop size bug for undocked servers.
    - Added logic to not restore the saved window position if the window would not be visible, e.g. if a display is disconnected.
    - Added a warning when attempting to add a server to a file without first adding a group.
    </releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
</package>